to compile:

rm -f main
c++ -Wall -I. `root-config --cflags` -o main main.cc                              \
  Event.cc EventSource.cc EventReadFromFile.cc  \
  AnalysisSteering.cc EnergyDist.cc BraggStatistic.cc EventDump.cc `root-config --libs`

or

compile

